record_data.record_title: MPU & MISO Monthly SSR Payment for Lakefront Unit No. 9
record_data.record_plain_text:
Monthly System Support Resource Payment for Lakefront Unit No. 9
Manitowoc Public Utilities ("MPU") and the Midcontinent Independent System Operator, Inc. ("MISO"), are parties to a "Standard Form System Support Resource ("SSR") Agreement Between Manitowoc Public Utilities and Midcontinent Independent System Operator, Inc." that was accepted by the Federal Energy Regulatory Commission on March 21, 2023, in Docket No. ER23-914-000 and designated as Original Service Agreement No. 6522 under MISO's Open Access Transmission, Energy and Operating Reserve Markets Tariff, with an effective date of February 1, 2023.
Section 9 and Exhibit 2 to the SSR Agreement provide for both hourly compensation and a fixed monthly system support resource payment ("Monthly SSR Payment"). The rate for hourly compensation has been established in MISO's separate SSR Agreement filing in the docketed proceeding referenced above. This rate schedule pertains only to the Monthly SSR Payment that recovers costs not included in the rate for hourly compensation.
The Monthly SSR Payment is $880,000. All other terms and conditions are as set forth in the SSR Agreement.
